author: MiniWarGaming
description:
For years (18, to be more specific) Holly has toyed with the idea of collecting her own army, but nothing has ever tempted her as much as terrain. Will these modular tiles be the thing that pushes her to make the move from supporter to gamer? You be the judge. 

Check out the Kickstarter at MiniWarGaming.com/depths
title: She Can't Resist the Tiles
